Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,欢迎加入OCR小组 qq群906722936 字幕优先发布于群内
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:03.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在伦敦办事处归我负责了\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm running this London office now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:05.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我敢保证情况会有所好转的\N{\rYUANWEN}and I can assure you things will pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:06.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们基本上一个客户都没有\N{\rYUANWEN}We have exactly no clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:07.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们基本上一个客户都没有\N{\rYUANWEN}We have exactly no clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:12.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们现在的案件数量激增\N{\rYUANWEN}WILLIAM: We are experiencing an unprecedented level of cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:14.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,威廉 你来了\N{\rYUANWEN}ELIZA: William, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:15.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你看上去很累\N{\rYUANWEN}You look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:17.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你看上去很美\N{\rYUANWEN}You look beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:20.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我最怕的是会让我的手下\N{\rYUANWEN}WILLIAM: My biggest fear is that I am sending my men
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:21.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,陷入他们尚未准备好的处境\N{\rYUANWEN}into situations that they are ill- prepared for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:23.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这样下去 会有人受伤的\N{\rYUANWEN}Someone is going to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:05.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,波茨先生 波茨先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Potts! Mr. Potts!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,斯嘉丽小姐 下午好\N{\rYUANWEN}: Miss Scarlet- - good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:11.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,波茨先生 明天我要和威灵顿督查\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, Mr. Potts, tomorrow, I embark on a case
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一起处理一个案子\N{\rYUANWEN}with Inspector Wellington, and I require
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:15.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我现在需要你手里一具尸体的背景信息\N{\rYUANWEN}some background information on one of your cadavers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:18.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,斯嘉丽小姐 这都是有流程的\N{\rYUANWEN}There is such a thing as a protocol, Miss Scarlet,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我会将信息\N{\rYUANWEN}and as such, I will convey any information
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:21.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-直接转给督查  -我明白\N{\rYUANWEN}directly to the inspector. I do understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:23.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但希望我的参与\N{\rYUANWEN}but hopefully my involvement will hasten
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:25.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,能加快逮捕凶手\N{\rYUANWEN}the arrest of the perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.47,0:01:26.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我越快拿到信息\N{\rYUANWEN}The sooner I have this information,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:28.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他就会越快被绳之于法\N{\rYUANWEN}the sooner he will be behind bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:30.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这难道不比流程更重要吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Surely, that is more important than protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:33.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没什么比流程更重要 斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Nothing is more important than protocol, Miss Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.31,0:01:36.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在我约会要迟到了\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, I'm late for an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.02,0:01:38.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,日安\N{\rYUANWEN}Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:45.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,波茨先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Potts!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:47.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真是够了\N{\rYUANWEN}: God save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:50.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们基本上都是一家人了嘛 波茨先生\N{\rYUANWEN}: We are practically family now, Mr. Potts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我和艾薇的关系\N{\rYUANWEN}My relationship with Ivy will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:54.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是我的私事\N{\rYUANWEN}and always shall be a private matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:57.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,永远不该被人拿来当做讨价还价的工具\N{\rYUANWEN}It should never be used as a bargaining tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:02:01.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的话我就失陪了\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, if you will excuse me, I'm taking tea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:03.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要和好友希奥博尔德·特纳先生一起喝茶\N{\rYUANWEN}with my good friend Mr. Theobald Turner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:04.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们每隔一周的周三就会一起喝茶\N{\rYUANWEN}We take tea on alternate Wednesdays,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:07.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且我已经说过了 我都迟到了\N{\rYUANWEN}and as I've already said, I am late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:11.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希奥博尔德\N{\rYUANWEN}Theobald?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,让开 波茨先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Out of the way, Mr. Potts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以你没看见任何人离开现场\N{\rYUANWEN}So you saw no one leaving the scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:04.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我说过了 后门是开着的\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, as I said, the back door was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,凶手一定是从那逃跑的\N{\rYUANWEN}The perpetrator must have escaped from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我在跟波茨先生说话\N{\rYUANWEN}I was talking to Mr. Potts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:10.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们谁都没看见\N{\rYUANWEN}we saw no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.99,YUANWEN,,0,0,0,,JON\NPHELPS: Oh, good.\N{\rYIWEN}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:13.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你决定再次加入我们了\N{\rYUANWEN}You've decided to join us again,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布莱克警探\N{\rYUANWEN}Detective Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你感觉好点了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:17.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的长官\N{\rYUANWEN}: Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:20.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你最好赶紧适应血腥场面 孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}You'd better get used to the sight of blood, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:22.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是你未来25年里都要面对的生活\N{\rYUANWEN}This is your life for the next 25 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,第一次见到犯罪现场 我只能祝福他了\N{\rYUANWEN}First crime scene- - bless him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:28.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认为特纳先生倒地之前就已经死了\N{\rYUANWEN}I believe Mr. Turner was dead before he hit the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:30.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一个私家侦探\N{\rYUANWEN}Hm, a private detective
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:32.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在又成了业余医生了\N{\rYUANWEN}and now an amateur doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你可真高效呢 斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}How efficient you are, Miss Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想跟我讨论高效吗 菲尔普斯警探\N{\rYUANWEN}You wish to talk of efficiency, Detective Phelps,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:39.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,凶案发生一个多小时才来了一个警探\N{\rYUANWEN}when it took over an hour for the first constable to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:42.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在如果可以的话 我要继续观察现场了\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, if I may, I have some further observations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,小心血\N{\rYUANWEN}Do mind the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:53.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认为受害人在这被击中\N{\rYUANWEN}I believe the victim was hit here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:56.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,轰然倒地\N{\rYUANWEN}knocked to the floor with some force.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可怜的希奥博尔德显然是挣扎到商店前面\N{\rYUANWEN}POTTS: Poor Theobald clearly struggled to the front of the shop
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:02.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,求救来着\N{\rYUANWEN}to get help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,死因是头部遭到重击\N{\rYUANWEN}The cause of death was likely a blow to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:05.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你说完了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Have you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:08.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没有 后门有强行进入痕迹\N{\rYUANWEN}No- - the back door shows signs of forced entry,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现金箱被清空\N{\rYUANWEN}the cash box has been emptied,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:12.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,棺材上的一些黄铜把手也不见了\N{\rYUANWEN}and there are some brass handles missing from the coffins,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一切证据都指向抢劫 但是\N{\rYUANWEN}which all points to a robbery, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:16.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,奇怪的是 居然有人会抢劫\N{\rYUANWEN}It's strange that an undertaker
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:18.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一个殡仪业者\N{\rYUANWEN}would be the target of such a crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:19.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,尤其是考虑到他的能力水平\N{\rYUANWEN}particularly one of his caliber.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:22.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希奥博尔德是个很出色的从业者\N{\rYUANWEN}Theobald was an excellent undertaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:25.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的观察 斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, thank for your observations, Miss Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我相信我们自己也会得出这样的结论\N{\rYUANWEN}But I'm sure we would have come to that conclusion ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你同意吗 布莱克警探\N{\rYUANWEN}Wouldn't you agree, Detective Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是什么味儿\N{\rYUANWEN}: What's that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:34.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,楼下太平间的甲醛\N{\rYUANWEN}Uh, formaldehyde from the mortuary downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:39.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,马上把窗户关上\N{\rYUANWEN}Shut that window immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你会毁了重要证据的\N{\rYUANWEN}You're disturbing important evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是什么毛病\N{\rYUANWEN}PHELPS: What is wrong with you, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:47.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这可是犯罪现场啊\N{\rYUANWEN}This is a crime scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:50.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是 长官 抱歉 长官\N{\rYUANWEN}: Yes, sir- - sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,小时候一想到棺材上挂个铃铛\N{\rYUANWEN}As a child, the notion that the dead needed a bell
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:55.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是为了防止死者在里面醒过来 我就吓坏了\N{\rYUANWEN}in case they woke up in their coffin quite terrified me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:57.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,斯嘉丽小姐 虽然我很乐意\N{\rYUANWEN}PHELPS: Well, I'd love to stay and reminisce
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在这听你回忆童年\N{\rYUANWEN}about your childhood, Miss Scarlet,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:04:59.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我们也要开始观察犯罪现场并且进行推论了\N{\rYUANWEN}but we will come to our own observations and deductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:02.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我们也要开始观察犯罪现场并且进行推论了\N{\rYUANWEN}but we will come to our own observations and deductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:05.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我又恶心了长官\N{\rYUANWEN}I feel sick again, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:28.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,早上好 斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Good morning, Miss Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:30.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有人暗恋你啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Secret admirer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:34.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,早 克拉伦斯 没有 这是我给自己的礼物\N{\rYUANWEN}Good morning, Clarence, and no, just a little gift to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:36.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,给我的办公室添点颜色\N{\rYUANWEN}Some cheer for my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:39.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,需要我提醒你每一分钱都很重要吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Need I remind you, every shilling counts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:42.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,钱很快就会源源不断的 克拉伦斯\N{\rYUANWEN}The shillings will soon be pouring in, Clarence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:45.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,威灵顿督查已经答应给我个案子了\N{\rYUANWEN}Inspector Wellington has promised me a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:46.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我敢说到下周这时候\N{\rYUANWEN}And I'm quite sure by this time next week,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:48.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们的案子会越接越多的\N{\rYUANWEN}we shall have plenty more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:50.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,再说了 干这行 有必要提醒自己\N{\rYUANWEN}Besides, in this line of work, it's important
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:54.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,世界上还是有美好的东西的\N{\rYUANWEN}to remind oneself there is some beauty in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:56.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-早啊  -威灵顿督查\N{\rYUANWEN}Morning. Inspector Wellington.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:59.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我们正说起你呢  -我倒是希望你没有\N{\rYUANWEN}I was just talking about you. I'd really rather you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:01.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都是好话 我保证\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI good things, I can assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,既然如此 那就继续啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, in that case, don't let me stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你好吗 威廉  -挺好 谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}How are you, William? Fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你吸鼻子了\N{\rYUANWEN}You just sniffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:14.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以要么你对花敏感\N{\rYUANWEN}So, either you're allergic to these flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:15.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要么是你有坏消息\N{\rYUANWEN}or you have bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:22.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们 我们接到了上级的指令\N{\rYUANWEN}We've, uh, we've had a diktat from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:25.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,预算被进一步压缩\N{\rYUANWEN}Budgets are being further squeezed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:27.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,案件增加但人手却变少\N{\rYUANWEN}Fewer men on more cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:30.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,新手们在没有经过适当培训的情况下就匆忙上岗了\N{\rYUANWEN}Recruits are being rushed through without proper training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:35.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且不允许我们再请私家侦探了\N{\rYUANWEN}And, uh, and no more hiring of private investigators.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:38.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那个案子呢 你答应给我查的案子\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, what about the case? The one you promised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你 你明知道我有多需要那个案子  -是 相信我\N{\rYUANWEN}You're, you're aware how much I need it. Yes, believe me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:42.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也不想这样的\N{\rYUANWEN}that this is the last thing that I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:45.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道现在我的工作量有多大\N{\rYUANWEN}You have no idea of my present workload.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,既然你这么忙 那请我\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, if you're so busy, that's even more reason
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:48.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就更有必要了啊 威廉\N{\rYUANWEN}to hire me, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,抱歉 但这事我决定不了\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm sorry, but it's out of my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:53.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但如果事情有任何改变\N{\rYUANWEN}But if anything changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:56.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我肯定会第一个通知你 我保证\N{\rYUANWEN}then you will be the first to know, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:02.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听着 我得回去了 还有很多事要做呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Look, I should get back, I have a great deal of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:04.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真好\N{\rYUANWEN}Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:07.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你打算气我多久\N{\rYUANWEN}How long do you intend to be cross with me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:10.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,给我个大概时间就行\N{\rYUANWEN}A rough estimate will do
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:13.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不是气你 只是在气这个现状\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm not cross with you, it's just the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:19.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我真的很抱歉\N{\rYUANWEN}Really, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:42.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,早上好 斯嘉丽小姐 今天有案子吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, good morning, Miss Scarlet. Any cases today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:45.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没有 不过明天肯定有\N{\rYUANWEN}No, but tomorrow, I'm certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,今天有案子吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Anything today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:03.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,早 有案子要查吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Morning- - anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没 暂时还没有\N{\rYUANWEN}Uh, no, nothing as yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:52.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我希望你能冷静下来 巴纳巴斯 这些压力和紧张\N{\rYUANWEN}I do wish you would calm down, Barnabus- - all this stress
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都会严重影响你的血压\N{\rYUANWEN}and strain will play havoc on your blood pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:56.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,已经一周了 什么都没有\N{\rYUANWEN}It's been a week, and nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:59.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的朋友还躺在冷库里 等着下葬\N{\rYUANWEN}My friend still lies in cold store, awaiting burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:02.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们好像很忙\N{\rYUANWEN}They do seem rather busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:05.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,督查\N{\rYUANWEN}Ah, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,威灵顿督查\N{\rYUANWEN}Inspector Wellington.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,波茨先生 艾薇\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Potts, Ivy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:12.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,威灵顿督查 我们已经等了已经有段时间了\N{\rYUANWEN}Inspector Wellington, we've been waiting some time now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:14.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想跟菲尔普斯警探聊聊我朋友的死\N{\rYUANWEN}to speak to Detective Phelps about my friend's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:16.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希奥博尔德·特纳先生吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Theobald Turner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:18.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,菲尔普斯警探已经被派到\N{\rYUANWEN}Detective Phelps has been sent up north
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:20.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,北边办案区了 据我所知\N{\rYUANWEN}on police business, and as far as I'm aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:23.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,目前布莱克警探会负责该项调查\N{\rYUANWEN}Detective Black is now leading the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:25.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们能赶紧处理好这家伙吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Will you please deal with this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:27.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:30.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我能说句实话吗 督查\N{\rYUANWEN}May I be candid, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布莱克警探可没办法负责这起案件\N{\rYUANWEN}Detective Black is not equipped to lead this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:37.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他恐怕不适合负责任何案件\N{\rYUANWEN}He's not equipped to lead any case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我敢保证布莱克警探很快就到\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm sure that Detective Black will be available shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:40.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在请恕我失陪了\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, if you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:43.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-不 我  -看你脸都急红了\N{\rYUANWEN}No, ILook at the flush on those cheeks of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:46.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我可不想还没结婚就变寡妇 巴纳巴斯\N{\rYUANWEN}I won't be a widow before I'm married, Barnabus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:49.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我另外找人帮你\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll find someone else to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:52.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且我正好知道有这么一个人\N{\rYUANWEN}And I know just the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想请我吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You wish to hire me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:04.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伦敦警察厅的人\N{\rYUANWEN}: Well, the Metropolitan Police
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真该做好自己的本职工作\N{\rYUANWEN}really should be doing their job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:09.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我总是说 世风日下啊\N{\rYUANWEN}But as I always say, the world is going to hell in a handcart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,极端情况就要采取极端措施\N{\rYUANWEN}Desperate times call for desperate measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你能这么说\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,波茨先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Potts. Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我敢保证\N{\rYUANWEN}I can assure you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:19.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会尽一切努力解决这个案子的\N{\rYUANWEN}I will do my utmost to solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:21.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,作为你的新客户\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, as your new client,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:24.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要求你每天给我汇报调查进展\N{\rYUANWEN}I must insist on daily briefings for any developments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:29.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\rYUANWEN}I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:32.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那么 你知道是否有人\N{\rYUANWEN}So, do you know of anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:33.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,跟特纳先生有仇吗\N{\rYUANWEN}who might have had a grudge against Mr. Turner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:36.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许是跟他共事的人\N{\rYUANWEN}Someone he worked with, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:37.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但如果这就是抢劫呢\N{\rYUANWEN}But what if it was just a robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:40.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,清空的钱箱 被偷走的黄铜把手\N{\rYUANWEN}Missing cashbox, stolen brass handles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有这个可能 但我已经跟菲尔普斯警探说过了\N{\rYUANWEN}That is still a possibility, but as I told Detective Phelps,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:45.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,抢劫殡仪馆本就很奇怪\N{\rYUANWEN}a funeral parlor is an odd place to rob,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:47.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,尤其是一个明显经营不善的殡仪馆\N{\rYUANWEN}particularly one that was clearly on hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我之前说过了 希奥博尔德是个很出色的从业者\N{\rYUANWEN}As I said before, Theobald was an excellent undertaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:53.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,斯嘉丽小姐从不怀疑这一点 巴纳巴斯\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Scarlet is not doubting that for a moment, Barnabus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:57.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她只是需要考量所有可能性\N{\rYUANWEN}She just needs to consider all possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,回答你之前的问题\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, in answer to your question,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:05.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想不出有任何人会伤害希奥博尔德\N{\rYUANWEN}I can think of no one who'd wish to harm Theobald.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:07.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,至于同事\N{\rYUANWEN}As for work colleagues, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:08.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他基本上都是单干的\N{\rYUANWEN}he was increasingly working alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:11.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只在有需要时才雇佣帮手\N{\rYUANWEN}He hired in help only when he needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:14.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你有提过他妹妹\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, you did mention his sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:16.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哦对\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 谢谢 艾薇\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, thank, thank you, Ivy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,弗朗西斯卡·特纳小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Um, a Miss Francesca Turner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:24.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她住在布里斯托尔\N{\rYUANWEN}She resides in Bristol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想她应该来参加葬礼吧 但谁知道呢\N{\rYUANWEN}I presume she'll be at the funeral, but who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:29.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她为什么不会来\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, why wouldn't she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:31.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们已经多年不来往了\N{\rYUANWEN}They've been estranged for many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以作为希奥博尔德的遗嘱执行人\N{\rYUANWEN}Which is why, as executor to Theobald's will,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:36.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我很吃惊他竟然把\N{\rYUANWEN}I was surprised to learn that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:38.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,全副身家都留给她了\N{\rYUANWEN}he's left his entire business to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:43.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,上帝是我的光\N{\rYUANWEN}MINISTER: The Lord is my light
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是我的救赎\N{\rYUANWEN}and my salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我有何可惧\N{\rYUANWEN}Whom shall I fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:54.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,上帝是我生命的保障\N{\rYUANWEN}The Lord is the stronghold of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:57.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我有何可惧\N{\rYUANWEN}Of whom shall I be afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:00.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当恶人攻击我 吞噬我的时候\N{\rYUANWEN}When the wicked advance against me to devour me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:04.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是我的敌人也是我的对手\N{\rYUANWEN}it is my enemies and my foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我没看见有像\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't see any sign of the woman
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,特纳先生妹妹的女人\N{\rYUANWEN}who could be Mr. Turner's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就在那边的树旁\N{\rYUANWEN}POTTS: Over there, by the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:25.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不好意思 请问您是特纳先生的妹妹吗\N{\rYUANWEN}ELIZA: Excuse me, you're Mr. Turner's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:28.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我是  -弗朗西斯卡·特纳小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}I am- - Miss Francesca Turner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:30.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是伊莱沙·斯嘉丽\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Eliza Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:32.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请您节哀顺变\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm so sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:34.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,波茨先生提到你了\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Potts mentioned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:37.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一个女私家侦探\N{\rYUANWEN}A female private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:39.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这跟一个女殡仪师一样\N{\rYUANWEN}It seems almost as unlikely as a female undertaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:42.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不多见呢\N{\rYUANWEN}which I now seem to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:46.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 我听说你哥在遗嘱中把生意留给你了\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, I heard your brother left you the business in his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你有想到吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Was that something you were expecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:51.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得你应该已经有答案了吧\N{\rYUANWEN}I suspect you already know the answer to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:55.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是听说你们俩关系疏远\N{\rYUANWEN}I did hear the two of you were estranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:59.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还真是不浪费时间呢 斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}You do not waste time, do you, Miss Scarlet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:03.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,抱歉了 不过我的工作就是问问题\N{\rYUANWEN}: I apologize, but it is my job to ask questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:06.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且我这么着急也是有原因的\N{\rYUANWEN}and, well, my swiftness is for good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:09.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为我想知道你哥到底发生了什么事\N{\rYUANWEN}To find out what happened to your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:14.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我有20多年没见过希奥博尔德了\N{\rYUANWEN}I have not seen Theobald in over 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看来我们俩对彼此都有遗憾\N{\rYUANWEN}There is some regret there for both of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:20.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,毕竟他把这里的生意留给我了\N{\rYUANWEN}it seems, given that he left me the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:25.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你住在布里斯托尔吧 那你会搬到伦敦来吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You live in Bristol, I believe- - will you now move to London?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:28.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我可没打算做殡葬业\N{\rYUANWEN}: I've no inclination to become an undertaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我小时候在我父亲干这行的时候\N{\rYUANWEN}I had quite enough of that in my childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:31.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就已经受够了\N{\rYUANWEN}when my father ran the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:35.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会留在这直到把店铺卖出去\N{\rYUANWEN}I will stay for as long as it takes to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:38.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但这可能要花点时间\N{\rYUANWEN}But it may take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:41.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,遗嘱中有些条款我也要考虑一下\N{\rYUANWEN}There are clauses in the will which I must take into account.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:42.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比如呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Such as?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:49.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希奥博尔德指名让我不要卖给某家殡仪馆\N{\rYUANWEN}Theobald did not want me to sell to a particular funeral home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:51.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哈德卡斯尔\N{\rYUANWEN}Hardcastle's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:54.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这点很遗憾 因为据我的律师说\N{\rYUANWEN}Which is a shame, because, according to my solicitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:56.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们是唯一提出报价的一家\N{\rYUANWEN}they're the only ones to have made an offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:14:00.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你觉得你哥为什么会附加这个条件呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Why do you think your brother would make such a request?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:02.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希奥博尔德和约翰·哈德卡斯尔是\N{\rYUANWEN}Theobald and John Hardcastle had always been
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:06.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,多年的竞争对手 在我父亲那辈就已经如此了\N{\rYUANWEN}old business rivals, as our fathers were before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:08.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想这两家之间的关系\N{\rYUANWEN}I can only imagine things had somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:09.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可能是更恶化了吧\N{\rYUANWEN}festered further between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:13.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,告辞了斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我设法收集了一些\N{\rYUANWEN}I've managed to garner some information
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:28.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,关于哈德卡斯尔殡仪馆负责人的信息\N{\rYUANWEN}on Hardcastle's Funeral Directors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还好吗 克拉伦斯\N{\rYUANWEN}Are you quite well, Clarence?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:35.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还好 还好\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, yes, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我 我说服了殡仪馆同业协会的职员\N{\rYUANWEN}I, I persuaded the clerk of the Funeral Directors' Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:39.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和我一起喝了一杯\N{\rYUANWEN}to have a drink with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:43.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的原则是滴酒不沾 但是\N{\rYUANWEN}I am, as a rule, teetotal, but, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想为了公司\N{\rYUANWEN}I thought I should do what I could
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:46.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也只能这么做了\N{\rYUANWEN}for the sake of the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还真是足智多谋呢\N{\rYUANWEN}How very resourceful of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:50.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你发现什么了\N{\rYUANWEN}And what did you find out from this drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:53.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哈德卡斯尔最近这些年\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, Hardcastle's have expanded extremely quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:54.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,生意扩张的非常迅速\N{\rYUANWEN}over recent years,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:57.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在城里买下了几家小的殡仪馆\N{\rYUANWEN}buying up smaller funeral homes across the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:00.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但有关他们玩忽职守的传言\N{\rYUANWEN}But rumors of malpractice
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:02.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,像臭味一样挥之不去\N{\rYUANWEN}have followed them round like a bad smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:09.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那个职员告诉我 有很多人\N{\rYUANWEN}The clerk told me that there had been numerous complaints
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:12.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,向同业协会投诉这家公司\N{\rYUANWEN}against the firm to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:15.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,最近的一起投诉是来自阿尔伯特·埃德蒙兹的\N{\rYUANWEN}The latest was, um, from an Albert Edmunds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:18.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是哈德卡斯尔之前的雇员\N{\rYUANWEN}He's a former employee of Hardcastle's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我有他的地址\N{\rYUANWEN}I have his address.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:24.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许我需要稍微躺会儿\N{\rYUANWEN}Perhaps I need a little lie- down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我从没见过特纳先生\N{\rYUANWEN}EDMUNDS: Oh, I never met Mr. Turner,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:34.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但是我听人提过他好几次\N{\rYUANWEN}but I heard mention of him a number of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:36.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道哈德卡斯尔先生一直想收购他们\N{\rYUANWEN}I know Mr. Hardcastle was determined
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:38.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但是特纳先生却不肯卖\N{\rYUANWEN}to take over the business, but Mr. Turner wouldn't sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听说你对前雇主提起过投诉\N{\rYUANWEN}So, you filed a complaint against your former employer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:46.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我 我当时是哈德卡斯尔先生的一名学徒\N{\rYUANWEN}I, I was an apprentice for Mr. Hardcastle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我都看到了\N{\rYUANWEN}I saw it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他让人们购买高昂的丧葬服务\N{\rYUANWEN}Him making people pay for funerals they couldn't afford,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:51.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当人们支付不起他就介绍放贷的给他们\N{\rYUANWEN}introducing them to moneylenders,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等他们还不起贷款时\N{\rYUANWEN}and when they couldn't afford the payments,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:57.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就有歹徒去找他们麻烦 比他们还钱 恐吓\N{\rYUANWEN}thugs were sent round to make them payintimidation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:58.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,砸窗户\N{\rYUANWEN}smashing windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那殡仪馆同业协会呢 他们怎么说\N{\rYUANWEN}And the Funeral Directors Guild, what did they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:01.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不想理\N{\rYUANWEN}Didn't want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哈德斯卡尔先生把他们都拿捏了\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Hardcastle has them in his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:05.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以你才离开公司的吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is that why you left the company?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:08.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我被毫无缘由的开除了\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, I was dismissed for no good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:10.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哈德卡斯尔先生的一位助手告诉我\N{\rYUANWEN}I was just told by one of Mr. Hardcastle's assistants
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:14.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,说公司不再需要我了\N{\rYUANWEN}that I was no longer needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果我要寻找\N{\rYUANWEN}If I was looking for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:17.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杀死特纳先生的凶手\N{\rYUANWEN}who had cause to kill Mr. Turner,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:22.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哈德卡斯尔先生肯定是我的首选\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Hardcastle would be the top of my list.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:28.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你给我这个机会\N{\rYUANWEN}ELIZA: Thank you for allowing me this access.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这些信息很有用\N{\rYUANWEN}It's, it's most useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:33.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希奥博尔德和我虽然不合\N{\rYUANWEN}Theobald and I may not have seen eye to eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我还是希望\N{\rYUANWEN}but I still want
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:38.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伤害他的人能被绳之于法\N{\rYUANWEN}whoever harmed him to face justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:40.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们为什么不合呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Why did you not see eye to eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:42.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一家人不就是这样吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You know how it is with family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:46.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没人能像你的至亲一样让你心烦了\N{\rYUANWEN}No one can vex you like your own flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:51.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果我父亲看到我现在的样子\N{\rYUANWEN}If my father could see me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:53.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,成为家族企业的所有人 不知作何感想\N{\rYUANWEN}Owner of the family business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你父亲呢\N{\rYUANWEN}And your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:17:01.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得他一定不会同意你干这行吧\N{\rYUANWEN}I cannot imagine he approves of your line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:04.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我父亲是个警察\N{\rYUANWEN}My father was a police officer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,后来成了私家侦探\N{\rYUANWEN}and later a private investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:09.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是个很开明的人 但是他不想我也过这种生活\N{\rYUANWEN}He was an enlightened man, but he didn't want this life for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他知道这是很难走的一条路\N{\rYUANWEN}He knew it would be a difficult path.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:18.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在每个家庭里 都会有个足智多谋的女人\N{\rYUANWEN}In every household, there is at least one resourceful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:20.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果更多我们这样的人被社会所接受\N{\rYUANWEN}If more of us were accepted,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:22.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,波茨先生可能就\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Potts's lament that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:24.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不会再有\N{\rYUANWEN}the world is going to hell in a handcart
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,世风日下的论调了\N{\rYUANWEN}might no longer be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,特纳小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Turner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:41.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一位玻璃工人两次被请来更换同一扇窗玻璃\N{\rYUANWEN}A glazier hired to replace the same windows twice,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,中间间隔三周\N{\rYUANWEN}three weeks apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:48.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哈德卡斯尔的一个前雇员跟我说\N{\rYUANWEN}One of Hardcastle's former employees told me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:52.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他最喜欢威胁别人\N{\rYUANWEN}intimidation was his trademark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:54.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想你哥可能曾被人威胁要他卖店铺\N{\rYUANWEN}I believe your brother was being pressured to sell,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:57.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而砸碎窗玻璃就是其中一个手段\N{\rYUANWEN}and breaking windows was one such tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:08.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,克拉伦斯 我想让你给\N{\rYUANWEN}Clarence, I want you to send a message
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,威灵顿督查送个信儿\N{\rYUANWEN}to Inspector Wellington.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看特纳先生是否曾对\N{\rYUANWEN}See if Mr. Turner filed a complaint
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:15.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,店铺窗户被砸一事提起过投诉\N{\rYUANWEN}about his windows being smashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还有 看看你能不能\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, and, um, see if you can get me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,帮我拿到谋杀档案的复印件\N{\rYUANWEN}copies of the murder file.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:21.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我虽然不指望布莱克警探\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't hold out much hope that Detective Black
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:22.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,会调查的非常全面\N{\rYUANWEN}has been particularly comprehensive
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:24.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但这种事\N{\rYUANWEN}in his investigation so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:26.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谁也说不好对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}but, uh, you never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:27.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怎么了\N{\rYUANWEN}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:29.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,门口台阶上有人留了一束花\N{\rYUANWEN}Uh, some flowers were left for you on the doorstep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:32.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问是威灵顿督查\N{\rYUANWEN}Inspector Wellington, no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:34.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他不喜欢我们吵架\N{\rYUANWEN}He does hate it when we're at odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:35.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,花不是督查送来的\N{\rYUANWEN}They're not from the inspector,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:38.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也不是任何对你心存好感的人送的\N{\rYUANWEN}nor from anyone else who wishes you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:41.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认为这是威胁\N{\rYUANWEN}It is, I, I believe, a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:47.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伊莱莎\N斯嘉丽\N愿您安息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:05.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真是够了 你能把这位先生\N{\rYUANWEN}God's sake- - can you please remove
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,从走廊里挪走吗\N{\rYUANWEN}this gentleman from the corridor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果有必要就关牢里去\N{\rYUANWEN}Put him in a cell if you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是 长官\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,长官 我有斯嘉丽小姐的口信\N{\rYUANWEN}Sir, I have a message from Miss Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:16.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是询问殡仪馆案件的\N{\rYUANWEN}It's a question about the undertaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布莱克警探负责这起案子的调查\N{\rYUANWEN}Detective Black is leading that investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:19.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-转交给他吧  -实际上 长官\N{\rYUANWEN}Give it to him. Actually, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:21.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他提交辞职报告了\N{\rYUANWEN}he handed in his notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-一次犯罪现场对他来说已经够了 所以  -查理呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Um, one crime scene was enough for him, so...Where's Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:25.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,菲尔普斯警探还在利兹调查干草市场的案子\N{\rYUANWEN}Detective Phelps is still in Leeds on the Haymarket case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:26.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,行吧 去把档案拿给我\N{\rYUANWEN}Fine, get me the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:28.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看来这事得我利用空闲时间\N{\rYUANWEN}It seems like I'll be doing this myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:30.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-亲自来了  -非常好 长官\N{\rYUANWEN}with all my spare time. Very good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:34.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还有别的事吗 警探\N{\rYUANWEN}And was there something else, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:39.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\N{\rYUANWEN}Actually, yes, um, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:42.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在纽约有个机会\N{\rYUANWEN}An opportunity has arisen, in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:44.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们想借调苏格兰场的一个警探\N{\rYUANWEN}They've invited a detective from Scotland Yard
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:47.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,加入他们的部门 为期一年\N{\rYUANWEN}to join their police department for a year's secondment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:50.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,长官 我想申请\N{\rYUANWEN}Sir. And I thought about applying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:51.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你觉得如何 长官\N{\rYUANWEN}What do you think, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得我最不希望的就是又少一个人手\N{\rYUANWEN}I think the last thing I need is to be another man down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:56.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那是当然\N{\rYUANWEN}: Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:57.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也意识到这时候\N{\rYUANWEN}I realize this might not have been
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,提这事可能不太合适\N{\rYUANWEN}the best time to mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:00.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,奥利弗 如果你是想问我是否会支持你的申请\N{\rYUANWEN}Oliver, if you're asking whether I will support your application,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:02.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,奥利弗 如果你是想问我是否会支持你的申请\N{\rYUANWEN}Oliver, if you're asking whether I will support your application,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:04.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我当然会 也许我们可以\N{\rYUANWEN}then, of course, I will- - perhaps we can find
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:07.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,另找个方便的时间来讨论这事\N{\rYUANWEN}a more convenient time to discuss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:09.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然 长官\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, sir, of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:13.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那这档案\N{\rYUANWEN}So, this file?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是 是 长官\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes! Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,曼娜斯小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}HARDCASTLE: Miss Manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:48.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是我 您一定是哈德卡斯尔先生吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes- Mr. Hardcastle, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:52.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我对你姑姥姥的去世深表哀悼\N{\rYUANWEN}My condolences on the passing of your great- aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:56.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的助手跟我说你希望\N{\rYUANWEN}My assistant informed me you were hoping
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我能亲自接手\N{\rYUANWEN}I would personally handle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:21:00.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,葬礼的日常事务\N{\rYUANWEN}the day- to- day arrangements of the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:02.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但鉴于我的工作量\N{\rYUANWEN}But due to my workload,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:04.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这对我来说恐怕不太可能\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm afraid that's not going to be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:06.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-可惜  -但这位阿什利先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, no. But Mr. Ashley here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,会负责你的业务\N{\rYUANWEN}will look after you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:11.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,并且为你提供昼夜不间断的服务\N{\rYUANWEN}and provide you with round- the- clock assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很高兴能认识你\N{\rYUANWEN}It was nice to have met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:17.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 如果我不能\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, well, if I cannot rely on the services
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:19.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,依靠公司负责人的服务\N{\rYUANWEN}of the director in charge of the company,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:21.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那尽管我十分不情愿 也只能另寻别处了\N{\rYUANWEN}then it is with a heavy heart that I must go elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:23.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真是太遗憾了\N{\rYUANWEN}: Which is such a shame,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:25.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为我本来想\N{\rYUANWEN}since I did so want
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:29.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,给心爱的姑姥姥用上城里最好的殡仪服务公司\N{\rYUANWEN}the best in town to oversee the funeral of my beloved aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:31.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,届时将有\N{\rYUANWEN}There'll be people of great influence
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,重要人物出席\N{\rYUANWEN}and import in attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:35.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会不惜一切代价搞好葬礼\N{\rYUANWEN}No expense will be spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:38.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,曼娜斯小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}: Um, do you know, Miss Manners,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:41.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想我可以重新安排我的日程\N{\rYUANWEN}I believe I can rearrange
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:43.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来专门为你服务\N{\rYUANWEN}some of my schedule to accommodate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:46.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:53.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是我们的高档系列\N{\rYUANWEN}This is from our premium range.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:56.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,用加拿大最好的榆木手工制作\N{\rYUANWEN}Handmade from the finest Canadian elm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:21:59.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,内衬的精致缎面\N{\rYUANWEN}Lined with exquisite satin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:01.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来自巴黎最好的制造商\N{\rYUANWEN}from the very best manufacturers in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:05.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,的确很不错\N{\rYUANWEN}It's very nice, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:09.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,打扰一下 先生 有个来自苏格兰场的\N{\rYUANWEN}Excuse me, sir- there's an Inspector Wellington
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:10.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,威灵顿督查来找您\N{\rYUANWEN}here from Scotland Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.92,0:22:13.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怎么来这了\N{\rYUANWEN}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:15.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你认识曼娜斯小姐吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you know Miss Manners?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:17.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:21.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,三年前 你协助调查了\N{\rYUANWEN}Three years ago, you assisted with an investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:24.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的马车失窃案 就在邦德街\N{\rYUANWEN}into a theft from my carriage on Bond Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:27.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,曼娜斯小姐 还记得吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Manners, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.03,0:22:30.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,曼娜斯小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:33.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 我现在想起来了\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:36.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,斯嘉丽小姐 你怎么来这了\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Scarlet, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.74,0:22:40.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谁是斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Who is Miss Scarlet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.08,0:22:47.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么叫她是个私家侦探\N{\rYUANWEN}What do you mean, she's a private detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:49.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认为斯嘉丽小姐正在调查\N{\rYUANWEN}I believe Miss Scarlet is investigating the case
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:52.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希奥博尔德·特纳先生死亡一案\N{\rYUANWEN}of the dead Mr. Theobald Turner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.97,0:22:55.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,跟我一样\N{\rYUANWEN}As am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.09,0:22:57.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们注意到\N{\rYUANWEN}: It's come to our attention
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:00.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你曾给特纳先生施加压力让他卖店铺\N{\rYUANWEN}that you were putting pressure on Mr. Turner to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:02.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他曾经提起投诉\N{\rYUANWEN}He filed a complaint about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:03.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,说店铺的窗玻璃被人砸碎\N{\rYUANWEN}some windows of his being smashed,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:06.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且他认为此事与你有关\N{\rYUANWEN}and he believed that that was connected to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:07.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这可太胡扯了\N{\rYUANWEN}What nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:09.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我对窗玻璃被砸一事一无所知\N{\rYUANWEN}I know nothing of any windows being broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.73,0:23:13.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们之间完全是良性竞争\N{\rYUANWEN}There was merely a healthy rivalry between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.07,0:23:17.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一个前雇员声称\N{\rYUANWEN}A former employee claims that you sell funeral plans
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.32,0:23:20.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你把葬礼计划卖给无力偿还的穷人\N{\rYUANWEN}to the poor who cannot afford the repayments.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.41,0:23:21.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后又介绍他们\N{\rYUANWEN}You then introduce them
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:23.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去借钱 随后对于拖欠不还的人\N{\rYUANWEN}to a moneylender, who uses strong- arm tactics
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:25.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,采取强硬手段\N{\rYUANWEN}when they default on what they owe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:27.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你说的是阿尔伯特·埃德蒙兹吧\N{\rYUANWEN}You speak of Albert Edmunds?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:29.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我跟你说吧 那不过是他被开除\N{\rYUANWEN}Let me tell you, it's nothing more
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:31.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以才捏造出来的谣言\N{\rYUANWEN}than sour grapes on account of his dismissal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:33.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那个人真是一无是处\N{\rYUANWEN}The man was useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:36.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,上周二早上你在哪里\N{\rYUANWEN}Where were you on the morning of Tuesday
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:38.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哈德卡斯尔先生\N{\rYUANWEN}last week, Mr. Hardcastle?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.14,0:23:43.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不是真想要我的不在场证明吧\N{\rYUANWEN}You are not seriously asking me to give you an alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:50.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我带着妻子孩子从伊斯特本的\N{\rYUANWEN}I was coming back from a family gathering in Eastbourne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:52.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一次家庭聚会回来\N{\rYUANWEN}with my wife and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:57.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不知道你能不能认出这个来\N{\rYUANWEN}I wonder if you could identify this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.28,0:24:01.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,昨天有人把这张卡片和鲜花一起留在门口\N{\rYUANWEN}It came with some flowers that were left for me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:04.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很明显是个警告\N{\rYUANWEN}Clearly a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.20,0:24:06.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡片跟你们公司用的相符 不是吗\N{\rYUANWEN}The card matches those used by your firm, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:10.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很明显是有人想诬陷我\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, clearly, someone is trying to defame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:13.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我为什么要用有自己公司印记的卡片呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Why on Earth would I use my own calling card?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.59,0:24:20.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别怪我\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.35,0:24:22.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只是说你的那个布莱克警探\N{\rYUANWEN}All I am saying is that your Detective Black
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.51,0:24:24.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很明显错过了特纳先生\N{\rYUANWEN}clearly missed evidence that Mr. Turner
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.31,0:24:26.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,曾被哈德卡斯尔威胁过的事实\N{\rYUANWEN}was being intimidated by Hardcastle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.06,0:24:28.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他不是我的布莱克警探 我都不怎么认识他\N{\rYUANWEN}He's not my Detective Black- I hardly knew the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.56,0:24:32.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是从埃塞克斯郡被征召来解决人力不足问题的\N{\rYUANWEN}He was drafted in from Essex to address the lack of manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.11,0:24:34.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们需要至少15名有经验的警探\N{\rYUANWEN}We need at least 15 experienced detectives,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.98,0:24:38.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可上头却只派了一个还没脱制服的新人\N{\rYUANWEN}and the super sent us one barely out of uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.15,0:24:40.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你最近去过苏格兰场吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Have you been in to Scotland Yard recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.20,0:24:42.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,连前台都进不去 一片混乱\N{\rYUANWEN}You can hardly get into reception- - it's chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.53,0:24:45.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你接手了这个案子 威廉\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm very pleased you've taken on the case, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.91,0:24:47.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但既然你这么忙\N{\rYUANWEN}But if you're so busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.75,0:24:49.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那当初你就不该同意\N{\rYUANWEN}you should never have agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.21,0:24:51.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,停用私家侦探服务\N{\rYUANWEN}to stop using the services of private investigators.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.21,0:24:53.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以你还是在怪我咯\N{\rYUANWEN}So, you are blaming me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.42,0:24:55.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我总得找个人怪吧\N{\rYUANWEN}I have to blame someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.22,0:25:00.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那你还发现什么了\N{\rYUANWEN}ELIZA: So, what else have you found out?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.84,0:25:03.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有个目击者看到一名身材魁梧\N{\rYUANWEN}That there was a witness who saw a heavyset man
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.01,0:25:05.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,深色头发 脸颊上有明显伤疤的男子\N{\rYUANWEN}with dark hair and a prominent scar on his cheek
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.22,0:25:08.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在特纳的窗户被砸碎后离开了现场\N{\rYUANWEN}leaving the scene after Mr. Turner's windows were smashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.43,0:25:10.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听上去肯定不是哈德卡斯尔\N{\rYUANWEN}That certainly doesn't sound like Hardcastle,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.77,0:25:13.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而我们又没有证据是他指使人干的\N{\rYUANWEN}and we've no proof that he arranged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.94,0:25:18.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢有人威胁你这事\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't like the idea that someone is threatening you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.95,0:25:21.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我经常被人威胁 威廉\N{\rYUANWEN}I get threatened all the time, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.28,0:25:22.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我干这行的时间已经很长了\N{\rYUANWEN}Surely, I've been doing this job long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.62,0:25:23.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你应该早就适应了啊\N{\rYUANWEN}for you to be comfortable with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.74,0:25:25.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这种事我永远无法适应\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll never be comfortable with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.37,0:25:29.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}POTTS: Miss Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.91,0:25:32.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,督查也在啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.58,0:25:34.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-波茨先生  -波茨先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Potts. Mr. Potts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.92,0:25:37.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我 我是来听你的每日简报的\N{\rYUANWEN}I, I have come for my daily briefing,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.76,0:25:39.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\rYUANWEN}but, uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.63,0:25:42.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,从你的出现来看 督查\N{\rYUANWEN}Do I gather by your presence, Inspector,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.30,0:25:44.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是接手这个案子了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}that you are now involved in this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.22,0:25:45.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rYUANWEN}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.60,0:25:47.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那可太让我放心了\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, that's reassuring, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.60,0:25:49.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢 波茨先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, thank you, Mr. Potts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.60,0:25:51.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,知道有人欣赏我还是挺不错的\N{\rYUANWEN}It's nice to know that someone appreciates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.60,0:25:54.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,既然这样\N{\rYUANWEN}So, if that is the case, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.31,0:25:57.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那我就不再需要斯嘉丽小姐的协助了\N{\rYUANWEN}I no longer require Miss Scarlet's assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.57,0:26:00.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,首先 波茨先生 有什么问题请来问我\N{\rYUANWEN}Firstly, Mr. Potts, please address that question to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.86,0:26:03.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,第二 我要提醒你一下\N{\rYUANWEN}And secondly, may I remind you,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.16,0:26:04.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们可是签过合同的\N{\rYUANWEN}we have a contractual agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.99,0:26:07.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恐怕你是摆脱不了我的\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm afraid you are stuck with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.79,0:26:11.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是 我也该回苏格兰场了\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, well, I should get back to Scotland Yard
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.62,0:26:13.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们该简报就简报吧\N{\rYUANWEN}I'lI leave you to your briefing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.92,0:26:15.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢 威廉\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, thank you, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.75,0:26:18.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 谢谢 威 督查\N{\rYUANWEN}Ah, yes, thank you, Will...Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.51,0:26:26.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这么说特纳先生提过\N{\rYUANWEN}So, Mr. Turner did mention
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.10,0:26:28.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哈德卡斯尔曾试图威胁过他\N{\rYUANWEN}that Hardcastle had tried to intimidate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.64,0:26:32.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 偶尔提起过\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes- - on occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.14,0:26:34.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你却从没想过要告诉我\N{\rYUANWEN}But you never thought to mention that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.36,0:26:36.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我\N{\rYUANWEN}I did
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.98,0:26:39.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不想说我朋友的坏话\N{\rYUANWEN}I did not wish to speak ill of my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.53,0:26:42.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我觉得希奥博尔德对于\N{\rYUANWEN}But I felt Theobald had developed
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.61,0:26:44.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哈德卡斯尔先生有点过于痴迷了\N{\rYUANWEN}an unhealthy obsession with Mr. Hardcastle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.91,0:26:47.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,自己生意失败也怪他\N{\rYUANWEN}Blaming him for the failure of his business,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.87,0:26:50.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还有所有相关的事情\N{\rYUANWEN}and, oh, everything in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.87,0:26:52.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你如何定义痴迷呢\N{\rYUANWEN}What do you class as obsession?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.67,0:26:58.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有一次 他说自己正在汇编有关他的档案\N{\rYUANWEN}At one point, he said he was compiling a file on the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.17,0:27:00.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我越来越担心\N{\rYUANWEN}I had a rising concern
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.25,0:27:03.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希奥博尔德已经到了有点偏执的地步了\N{\rYUANWEN}that Theobald had become quite paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.39,0:27:12.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,进来 斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Come in, Miss Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.89,0:27:15.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,刚刚收拾完\N{\rYUANWEN}Just finishing off
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.02,0:27:17.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我哥的最后一批私人物品\N{\rYUANWEN}packing the last of my brother's personal effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.44,0:27:21.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你有没有发现你哥整理的\N{\rYUANWEN}Can I ask if you've found a certain file
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.86,0:27:23.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一份有关哈德斯卡尔先生的档案\N{\rYUANWEN}your brother kept on Mr. Hardcastle?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.74,0:27:25.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还真有\N{\rYUANWEN}I have, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.74,0:27:28.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我正打算拿到办公室去给你呢\N{\rYUANWEN}I was planning to bring it to your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.12,0:27:32.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但可不只是一份档案\N{\rYUANWEN}But it's more than just a file.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.75,0:27:40.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,向殡仪馆同业协会的投诉\N{\rYUANWEN}Complaints to the Funeral Directors Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.88,0:27:44.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,报纸上有关哈德卡斯尔做的广告\N{\rYUANWEN}Newspaper articles about Hardcastle's advertisements.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.26,0:27:46.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这么说 巴纳巴斯说的对\N{\rYUANWEN}So, Barnabus was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.47,0:27:47.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他的朋友特纳先生\N{\rYUANWEN}His friend Mr. Turner
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.84,0:27:49.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对哈德卡斯尔先生已经到了痴迷的地步\N{\rYUANWEN}was utterly obsessed with Mr. Hardcastle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.35,0:27:53.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他被人砸碎的窗户\N{\rYUANWEN}His broken windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.39,0:27:58.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这个应该是对应着我找到的给玻璃工的付款收据\N{\rYUANWEN}This must refer to the glazier's receipts I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.15,0:28:02.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他甚至列出了其它\N{\rYUANWEN}He even has a list of other undertakers
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.40,0:28:04.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,窗户也被砸碎的殡仪馆的名单\N{\rYUANWEN}who appear to have their windows smashed in the same manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.65,0:28:07.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他不仅痴迷而且很全面\N{\rYUANWEN}He was obsessed, and thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.24,0:28:12.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他甚至还留下了砖块\N{\rYUANWEN}He even kept the bricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.95,0:28:17.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们上面都有同一个缩写\N{\rYUANWEN}They all have the same initials on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.96,0:28:21.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,SP\N{\rYUANWEN}"S. P. "
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.10,0:28:37.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,打扰一下\N{\rYUANWEN}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.06,0:28:39.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是来找业主佩特洛夫先生的\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm, uh, looking for the proprietor, Mr. Petrov.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.77,0:28:42.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他出去干活了\N{\rYUANWEN}He's away from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.07,0:28:44.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那你能告诉我他什么时候回来吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, can you tell me when he'll be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.32,0:28:50.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他老婆过世了\N{\rYUANWEN}His wife, she died, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.11,0:28:51.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,几周后他女儿也走了\N{\rYUANWEN}Only weeks after, his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.99,0:28:53.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他状况不太好已经有几个月了\N{\rYUANWEN}He has not been in good way for months now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.58,0:28:55.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听你这么说我非常遗憾\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.37,0:28:57.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是来找他的一个顾客的\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm looking for one of his customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.83,0:29:00.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,深色头发 脸上有疤\N{\rYUANWEN}Dark hair, scar on his cheek?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.54,0:29:05.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不认识这个人\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't know this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.00,0:29:07.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我得回去工作了\N{\rYUANWEN}I must go back to work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.22,0:29:09.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我\N{\rYUANWEN}I've, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.22,0:29:11.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我拜访过一些殡仪馆\N{\rYUANWEN}visited a number of undertakers
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.22,0:29:13.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们的窗户都被\N{\rYUANWEN}who've had their windows smashed with bricks
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.30,0:29:15.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,刻着佩特洛夫名字首字母的砖块砸碎过\N{\rYUANWEN}engraved with Mr. Petrov's initials.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.31,0:29:18.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很明显他的生意和犯罪之间有联系\N{\rYUANWEN}It's clear there's a link to this business and the crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.52,0:29:21.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我还没告诉警方 但如果我的问题得不到答案\N{\rYUANWEN}I haven't yet told the police, but will be forced
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.98,0:29:26.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那我只能去找警察了\N{\rYUANWEN}to do so if my inquiries remain unanswered.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.11,0:29:28.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,佩特洛夫先生可能会被牵扯进来\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Petrov himself may be implicated in the crimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.19,0:29:30.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我敢说他肯定不想这样\N{\rYUANWEN}which is surely the last thing he needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.62,0:29:36.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,脸上有疤的那个人是放债的\N{\rYUANWEN}: The man with the scar is a moneylender.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.54,0:29:38.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,托马斯·马泽利\N{\rYUANWEN}Tomasz Mazelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.71,0:29:42.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,佩特洛夫先生欠他家人葬礼的钱\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Petrov owed him for his family's funerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.75,0:29:45.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他就过来定期收款\N{\rYUANWEN}He comes for regular payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.71,0:29:49.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,每次都会拿走一盒砖 从来不给钱\N{\rYUANWEN}Always takes a box of bricks, which he never pays for.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.31,0:30:01.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,告诉我 伊莱沙\N{\rYUANWEN}: Tell me, Eliza,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.81,0:30:04.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你觉得自己能学会敲门吗\N{\rYUANWEN}do you think that you'll ever learn to knock?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.23,0:30:06.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不能\N{\rYUANWEN}Um, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.57,0:30:08.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我已经查到了放债人托马斯·马泽利的\N{\rYUANWEN}I've secured the name and work address
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.74,0:30:11.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,名字和工作地址\N{\rYUANWEN}of the moneylender Tomasz Mazelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.49,0:30:13.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他在朗埃克附近有个办公室 走吧\N{\rYUANWEN}He has an office off Long Acre- - shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.07,0:30:15.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我手头还有很多其它案子要忙\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, I'm busy with a great deal of other cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.62,0:30:18.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,包括干草市场的一起备受瞩目的抢劫案 所以\N{\rYUANWEN}including that of a high- profile robbery in Haymarket, so,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.95,0:30:21.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只能等我有时间的时候再来处理你的案子了\N{\rYUANWEN}I will come to your case when I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.62,0:30:24.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.17,0:30:26.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你会等我吗\N{\rYUANWEN}So you'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.13,0:30:28.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不会 威廉\N{\rYUANWEN}No, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.00,0:30:29.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但既然你都说了\N{\rYUANWEN}But as you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.51,0:30:31.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你太忙 没时间去见那个\N{\rYUANWEN}you're too busy to go and see the man who was, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.72,0:30:33.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,给我送百合花并且\N{\rYUANWEN}almost probably the one who sent me those lilies
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.89,0:30:34.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,威胁过我的男人\N{\rYUANWEN}and threatened my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.89,0:30:36.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但\N{\rYUANWEN}But, uh
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.39,0:30:38.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想就算我一个人\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, I'm sure I'll be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.68,0:30:41.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去见这么个危险暴力的罪犯\N{\rYUANWEN}to visit such a dangerous, violent criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.77,0:30:45.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,应该也没问题吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.88,0:31:12.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是苏格兰场的威灵顿督查\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm Inspector Wellington from Scotland Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.55,0:31:15.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,托马斯·马泽利在吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Tomasz Mazelli around?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.14,0:31:21.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他出去了\N{\rYUANWEN}He's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.31,0:31:23.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道他什么时候回来吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, do you know when he'll be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.02,0:31:24.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不知道 亲\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't know, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.60,0:31:25.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是他什么人 太太吗\N{\rYUANWEN}What am I, his missus?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.98,0:31:29.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不是 你是他手下\N{\rYUANWEN}No, you're his clerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.23,0:31:31.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且如果你再对这位女士这么没礼貌的话\N{\rYUANWEN}And if you don't show the lady some courtesy,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.44,0:31:32.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们俩可能就得去小小黑屋\N{\rYUANWEN}then you and I will be talking alone
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.78,0:31:35.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,聊聊了\N{\rYUANWEN}in a dark room
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.20,0:31:38.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,保证没人看到\N{\rYUANWEN}with no witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.20,0:31:39.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请救救我\N{\rYUANWEN}MAN: Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.49,0:31:41.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,拜托了 不\N{\rYUANWEN}: Please, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.38,0:31:49.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,拜托 不 不 不\N{\rYUANWEN}MAN: Please! No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.42,0:31:52.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你应该就是托马斯·马泽利吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Tomasz Mazelli, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.05,0:31:55.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你被捕了\N{\rYUANWEN}You're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.84,0:31:56.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,埃德蒙兹先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Edmunds.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.26,0:32:00.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你认识他吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.01,0:32:02.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他曾为哈德卡斯尔工作过\N{\rYUANWEN}ELIZA: He worked for Hardcastle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.19,0:32:08.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不该报告哈德卡斯尔的事的\N{\rYUANWEN}I shouldn't have reported Hardcastle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.19,0:32:09.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这不是你的错\N{\rYUANWEN}ELIZA: This isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.81,0:32:12.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你得去看医生\N{\rYUANWEN}You need to see a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.28,0:32:13.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他去苏格兰场\N{\rYUANWEN}Can one be arranged
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.61,0:32:15.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,录口供的时候能叫个医生过去吗\N{\rYUANWEN}when he comes to Scotland Yard to make a statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.20,0:32:18.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我才不去录口供\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm not making a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.11,0:32:20.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我可以为你安排保护人员 没什么好怕的\N{\rYUANWEN}I can arrange protection- there's nothing to be scared of.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.49,0:32:22.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你说起来当然轻松\N{\rYUANWEN}That's easy for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.54,0:32:24.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只想不再被人骚扰\N{\rYUANWEN}I, I just want to be left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.04,0:32:27.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这跟一起谋杀案调查有关 先生\N{\rYUANWEN}This is part of a murder investigation, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.08,0:32:28.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我虽然不能强迫你起诉他\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, I can't force you to press charges,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.37,0:32:29.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但如果你能录份口供\N{\rYUANWEN}but I would appreciate it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.54,0:32:30.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会很感激你的\N{\rYUANWEN}if you'd at least make a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.88,0:32:32.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不想跟这事扯上任何关系\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't want anything to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.46,0:32:34.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,- 别来烦我埃   -德蒙兹先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Just let me bel Mr. Edmunds
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.84,0:32:36.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-别再来找我  -阿尔伯特\N{\rYUANWEN}Leave me alone! Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.34,0:32:38.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,拜托 放过我吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Please just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.76,0:32:41.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你一定能做些什么吧\N{\rYUANWEN}There must be something you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.60,0:32:44.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他又没被捕 我不能强迫他去警局\N{\rYUANWEN}He's not under arrest- - I can't force him to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.77,0:32:47.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们先看看马泽利友什么可说的吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's see what Mazelli has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.27,0:32:49.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,打扰一下先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Excuse me, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.15,0:32:50.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,给斯嘉丽小姐的口信\N{\rYUANWEN}A message for Miss Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.40,0:32:57.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我真是走到哪都躲不过这个人啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Is there nowhere I can hide from that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.37,0:33:06.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哦 斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh! Miss Scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.20,0:33:07.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我还担心你没收到我的纸条呢\N{\rYUANWEN}I feared you did not get my note.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.75,0:33:08.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我正要去亲自找你\N{\rYUANWEN}I was just on my way to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.96,0:33:10.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我已经尽快赶来了 波茨先生\N{\rYUANWEN}I came as quick as I could, Mr. Potts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.92,0:33:12.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还好吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Is all well?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.25,0:33:14.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一点都不好\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, not in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.09,0:33:16.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,特纳小姐来找我\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Turner came to see me,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.42,0:33:19.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,给了我希奥博尔德的一个旧棋盘游戏作为纪念\N{\rYUANWEN}to gift me an old board game of Theobald's.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.26,0:33:22.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这就让你不安了\N{\rYUANWEN}And this is what has upset you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.18,0:33:23.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\rYUANWEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.18,0:33:24.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是她告诉我的消息\N{\rYUANWEN}It was the news she imparted
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.39,0:33:25.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,造成了我的不安\N{\rYUANWEN}that caused me this distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.52,0:33:28.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,特纳小姐 违背了她\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Turner, contrary to the wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.27,0:33:30.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,已故兄长和我挚友\N{\rYUANWEN}of her deceased brother
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.10,0:33:31.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希奥博尔德的遗愿\N{\rYUANWEN}and my dear friend Theobald,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.81,0:33:33.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,打算将殡仪馆卖给哈德卡斯尔\N{\rYUANWEN}is to sell the funeral home to Hardcastle's.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.45,0:33:46.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你对希奥博尔德·特纳先生的谋杀案知道多少\N{\rYUANWEN}What do you know about the murder of Mr. Theobald Turner?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.41,0:33:48.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不认识他\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.41,0:33:51.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有证人看到你砸碎了特纳先生的窗玻璃\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, a witness has you smashing Mr. Turner's windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.37,0:33:52.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认为你是听从了另一个\N{\rYUANWEN}I believe that that was on the orders
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.96,0:33:55.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,殡仪馆业者约翰·哈德斯卡尔的命令才如此做的\N{\rYUANWEN}of another undertaker, John Hardcastle.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.96,0:33:59.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他我也不认识\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't know him, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.05,0:34:04.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,周二下午你在哪\N{\rYUANWEN}Where were you on Tuesday afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.14,0:34:09.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我在宽街酒店\N{\rYUANWEN}I was at the Broad Street Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.10,0:34:10.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去那喝酒了\N{\rYUANWEN}Went in for a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.94,0:34:13.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我喜欢那里的一个女招待\N{\rYUANWEN}I like one of the waitresses there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.53,0:34:20.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我\N{\rYUANWEN}: Oh, Ive, uh
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.82,0:34:23.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我过去处理过很多放债的\N{\rYUANWEN}I've dealt with many moneylenders in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.57,0:34:25.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,根据我的经验 他们所有人无一例外\N{\rYUANWEN}and it's my experience that all of them, bar none,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.78,0:34:27.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都非常讨厌\N{\rYUANWEN}have a deep aversion
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.62,0:34:30.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,向女王陛下的税务局缴纳税款\N{\rYUANWEN}to paying their dues to Her Majesty's Revenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.37,0:34:32.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而我确定你肯定知道\N{\rYUANWEN}And as I am sure you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.54,0:34:34.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,作为一名金融行业的商人\N{\rYUANWEN}as a businessman in the financial sector,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.79,0:34:40.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,逃税将被判处重刑监禁\N{\rYUANWEN}avoidance of tax contributions carries a hefty prison sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.80,0:34:43.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你抓不到我任何把柄的\N{\rYUANWEN}You won't find nothing on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.64,0:34:46.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,既然如此 如果我们对\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, in that case, you have nothing to fear
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.72,0:34:48.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你的生意进行调查\N{\rYUANWEN}whilst we undertake an investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.89,0:34:50.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你也没什么好怕的\N{\rYUANWEN}into your business dealings.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.98,0:34:52.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,与此同时 你的账户\N{\rYUANWEN}In the meantime, your accounts
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.89,0:34:54.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和所有资产将被冻结\N{\rYUANWEN}and all your assets will be frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.23,0:34:56.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别担心 不会太久的\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't worry, that won't take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.77,0:34:59.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有几个月应该就够了\N{\rYUANWEN}A couple of months should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.53,0:35:02.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想要什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.99,0:35:06.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,特纳先生出事那天你在哪\N{\rYUANWEN}Information about the day that Mr. Turner died.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.08,0:35:12.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我替哈德卡斯尔先生去了趟酒店\N{\rYUANWEN}I was at the hotel for Mr. Hardcastle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.29,0:35:15.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他被一个女人骚扰 很明显是\N{\rYUANWEN}He was being bothered by some woman he'd clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.58,0:35:17.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你明白吧\N{\rYUANWEN}You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.04,0:35:18.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,跟他有一腿的女人\N{\rYUANWEN}Been with.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.34,0:35:20.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他不想自己太太发现这事\N{\rYUANWEN}He didn't want his missus to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.96,0:35:23.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以就雇我去见她\N{\rYUANWEN}So, he hired me to pay her a visit
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.59,0:35:25.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,劝她离开这里\N{\rYUANWEN}to encourage her to leave the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.51,0:35:29.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我去了她的房间 402 但她一直没出现\N{\rYUANWEN}I went to her room, 402, but she never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.81,0:35:32.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她叫什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What was her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.48,0:35:36.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,女士\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.98,0:35:39.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是来找你们一位客人的 弗朗西斯卡·特纳小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm looking for one of your guests, a Miss Francesca Turner.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.65,0:35:44.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她住在402房间\N{\rYUANWEN}WILLIAM: She's in room 402.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.11,0:35:47.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,弗朗西斯卡·特纳和哈德卡斯尔有一腿\N{\rYUANWEN}Francesca Turner has been having an affair with Hardcastle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.70,0:35:51.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,特纳小姐已经退房了\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Turner has checked out, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.25,0:35:55.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,马泽利被派去警告特纳小姐的那天\N{\rYUANWEN}The day Mazelli was sent to warn Miss Turner off
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.50,0:35:57.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也是她哥哥被杀的那天\N{\rYUANWEN}was the day that her brother was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.42,0:35:59.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以那天她就已经到伦敦了 但她却从没提过\N{\rYUANWEN}So, she was in London that day, yet she never mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.84,0:36:02.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以她现在是我们的头号嫌犯\N{\rYUANWEN}Which makes her our prime suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.38,0:36:04.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,问题是 她去哪了呢\N{\rYUANWEN}The question is, where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.51,0:36:05.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,处理医嘱的律师\N{\rYUANWEN}The lawyer who dealt with the will
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.97,0:36:07.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,应该会有她在布里斯托尔的住址\N{\rYUANWEN}is likely to have her home address in Bristol.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.80,0:36:08.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们可以从他那要到\N{\rYUANWEN}We can get it from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.93,0:36:10.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那我找人送个信\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll send a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.68,0:36:13.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哈德卡斯尔既然费劲\N{\rYUANWEN}For Hardcastle to go to the effort
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.47,0:36:15.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,派马泽利去吓唬她\N{\rYUANWEN}of sending Mazelli to scare her,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.18,0:36:18.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,说明她想从他那里得到些什么\N{\rYUANWEN}it seems likely she must have wanted something from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.15,0:36:21.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,或者只是威胁他说要告诉他老婆\N{\rYUANWEN}Or just threatened to tell his wife about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.27,0:36:24.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们去问当事人就知道了\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's ask the man himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.78,0:36:32.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我有托马斯·马泽利的签名证词\N{\rYUANWEN}WILLIAM: I have a signed statement from Tomasz Mazelli implicating you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.29,0:36:35.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,暗示你在希奥博尔德·特纳先生\N{\rYUANWEN}in the intimidation of Mr. Theobald Turner
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.29,0:36:37.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,被谋杀前几周恐吓过他\N{\rYUANWEN}in the weeks leading up to his murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.50,0:36:39.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-恐吓  -证词里还指出\N{\rYUANWEN}Intimidation? ELIZA: The statement also claims
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.79,0:36:42.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你和弗朗西斯卡·特纳小姐关系亲密\N{\rYUANWEN}you were fraternizing with Miss Francesca Turner.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.50,0:36:45.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想你太太对此应该很感兴趣\N{\rYUANWEN}Something your wife might be interested to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.26,0:36:48.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你为什么要派托马斯·马泽利去吓唬她呢\N{\rYUANWEN}WILLIAM: Why did you send Tomasz Mazelli to scare her off?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.05,0:36:49.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她想从你这得到什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What did she want from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.01,0:36:53.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是我的私人事务\N{\rYUANWEN}It's a personal matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.43,0:36:54.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许我邀请哈德卡斯尔太太一起来聊\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, perhaps you'd feel more comfortable if we
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.97,0:36:59.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你会觉得更舒服\N{\rYUANWEN}invited Mrs. Hardcastle in to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.86,0:37:06.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我从未对我妻子不忠过\N{\rYUANWEN}I have never been unfaithful to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.20,0:37:11.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,弗朗西斯卡和我\N{\rYUANWEN}Francesca and I, it was more...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.99,0:37:13.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那都是20年前的事了\N{\rYUANWEN}More than 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.58,0:37:18.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是 当时我是跟我太太订了婚\N{\rYUANWEN}And yes, I was engaged to my wife at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.29,0:37:19.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但还没结婚\N{\rYUANWEN}but we weren't married.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.83,0:37:23.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可你最近见过特纳小小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}And yet you've seen Miss Turner recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.05,0:37:28.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她陷入了困境 过来找我借钱\N{\rYUANWEN}She'd fallen on hard times and come to me for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.93,0:37:31.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不想帮她\N{\rYUANWEN}When I was unwilling to help her out,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.26,0:37:33.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她就威胁说要告诉我太太\N{\rYUANWEN}she threatened to tell my wife about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.18,0:37:35.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我才派马泽利去的\N{\rYUANWEN}That's why I sent Mazelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.64,0:37:37.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就这么简单\N{\rYUANWEN}Plain and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.86,0:37:52.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你觉得特纳小姐去找他\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you believe it was money
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.62,0:37:54.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是为了钱吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Turner went to see him about?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.45,0:37:56.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有可能啊\N{\rYUANWEN}It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.91,0:37:59.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想既然她这么缺钱\N{\rYUANWEN}I suppose if she was desperate for money
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.29,0:38:01.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而哈德卡斯尔又拒绝了她\N{\rYUANWEN}and Hardcastle refused,
