Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.59,0:38:07.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,感觉还是有不对劲的地方\N{\rYUANWEN}Something still feels amiss here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.59,0:38:10.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等等布里斯托尔那边的消息吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, let's see what comes back from Bristol.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.30,0:38:11.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只要特纳小姐一到家\N{\rYUANWEN}As soon as Miss Turner arrives home,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.80,0:38:13.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,警察就会在家里等着她\N{\rYUANWEN}the police will be waiting for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.85,0:38:15.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rYUANWEN}: Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.18,0:38:18.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我需要向上级汇报干草市场抢劫案的最新情况了\N{\rYUANWEN}Ineed to update the super on the Haymarket robbery.
