Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.10,0:38:23.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 伊莱沙 这地方没人睡觉的\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, Eliza, this place never sleeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.35,0:38:24.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,回家去吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.73,0:38:26.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们明早再继续 好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}We'll pick this up in the morning, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.41,0:38:35.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,督查呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Where's the inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.66,0:38:37.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我有关于特纳小姐的口信要给他\N{\rYUANWEN}I have a message regarding Miss Turner.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.91,0:38:39.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么 他们找到她了\N{\rYUANWEN}What, they found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.50,0:38:41.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没有 但是布里斯托尔警局跟她的邻居聊过\N{\rYUANWEN}No, but the Bristol police spoke to her neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.75,0:38:43.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他说特纳小姐18年前\N{\rYUANWEN}He said Miss Turner moved in
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.50,0:38:45.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,跟丈夫刚结婚那会搬过来的\N{\rYUANWEN}when she married her husband 18 years previous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.38,0:38:47.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她丈夫今年早些时候过世了\N{\rYUANWEN}Her husband passed earlier this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.34,0:38:49.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嘿 少爷 有事找你\N{\rYUANWEN}PHELPS: Oi, his lordship! I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.09,0:38:50.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,查理 不知道你回来了\N{\rYUANWEN}Charlie- - didn't know you were back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.97,0:38:53.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想我了是吧 真感动\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss me, did you? Oh, I'm touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.18,0:38:55.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别再对斯嘉丽小姐抛媚眼了\N{\rYUANWEN}Now stop batting your eyelashes at Miss Scarlet
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.05,0:38:56.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,赶紧过来\N{\rYUANWEN}and get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.89,0:38:59.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你去吧\N{\rYUANWEN}You go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.10,0:39:00.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我把这个给威灵顿督查\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll give it to Inspector Wellington.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.23,0:39:12.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,弗朗西斯卡·特纳嫁给了彼得·埃德蒙兹\N{\rYUANWEN}"Francesca Turner married a Peter Edmunds..."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.45,0:39:16.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,埃德蒙兹\N{\rYUANWEN}Edmunds.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.95,0:39:20.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,阿尔伯特·埃德蒙兹\N{\rYUANWEN}Albert Edmunds.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.29,0:39:24.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,打扰一下\N{\rYUANWEN}Excuse me. Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.79,0:39:26.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这里有位埃德蒙兹先生吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is a Mr. Edmunds here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.71,0:39:28.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没在 亲\N{\rYUANWEN}No, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.17,0:39:29.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我正要去接他和他母亲\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm picking up him and his mother next.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.92,0:39:32.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去哪接他们\N{\rYUANWEN}You're picking them up from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.99,0:39:59.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,稍等 斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}: One moment, Miss Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.78,0:40:01.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,稍等斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}: One moment, Miss Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.29,0:40:08.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我时间不多\N{\rYUANWEN}Cannot talk for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.79,0:40:12.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,马车已经过来准备送我去火车站了\N{\rYUANWEN}Carriage is on its way to take me to the railway station.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.34,0:40:13.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你和你儿子\N{\rYUANWEN}You and your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.76,0:40:19.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道你是阿尔伯特·埃德蒙兹的母亲了\N{\rYUANWEN}I know you are Albert Edmunds'mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.68,0:40:20.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,特纳小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Turner.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.18,0:40:25.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而我现在想\N{\rYUANWEN}And I'm right in thinking that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.89,0:40:28.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他的父亲应该是哈德卡斯尔先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Hardcastle is his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.02,0:40:34.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以你才找他要钱\N{\rYUANWEN}That's why you went to him for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.24,0:40:41.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.33,0:40:43.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,阿尔伯特是我儿子\N{\rYUANWEN}Albert is my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.75,0:40:46.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但那是我和彼得·埃德蒙兹的儿子\N{\rYUANWEN}But from my marriage to Peter Edmunds,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.54,0:40:47.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他父亲过世了\N{\rYUANWEN}who is now deceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.54,0:40:52.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们结婚只有18年\N{\rYUANWEN}You were only married to him for 18 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.92,0:40:54.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可我看记录 阿尔伯特今年21岁\N{\rYUANWEN}I checked the census- - Albert is 21.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.14,0:41:01.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想你当初离开伦敦\N{\rYUANWEN}I believe you left London
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.51,0:41:03.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是因为你怀孕了\N{\rYUANWEN}because you became pregnant by a man
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.26,0:41:07.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而那个男人却不被你父亲和你哥所接受\N{\rYUANWEN}both your father and brother despised.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.19,0:41:09.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以你们关系才不好的 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}That's why you were estranged, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.23,0:41:14.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你哥被杀那天\N{\rYUANWEN}You were also in London
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.19,0:41:16.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你已经到伦敦了\N{\rYUANWEN}the day of your brother's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.62,0:41:26.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你去找哈德卡斯尔是为了找你儿子 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}You went to Hardcastle to look for your son, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.58,0:41:30.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但他拒绝了你\N{\rYUANWEN}But he turned you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.25,0:41:31.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后呢 你就去找了你哥\N{\rYUANWEN}So then what? You went to your brother
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.92,0:41:33.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看他知不知道阿尔伯特的下落 是\N{\rYUANWEN}to see if he knew where Albert was, is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.51,0:41:36.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是这样吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is that what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.30,0:41:41.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当我 当我见到我哥\N{\rYUANWEN}When I, when I saw my brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.26,0:41:43.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,过去的积怨让我俩都失去了理智\N{\rYUANWEN}the resentment from the past, it gripped us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.89,0:41:45.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们 我们吵了起来\N{\rYUANWEN}We had, we had an argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.06,0:41:49.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我很生气 然后\N{\rYUANWEN}: I became angry, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.77,0:41:54.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,推倒了他\N{\rYUANWEN}: Pushed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.15,0:41:56.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不是故意的\N{\rYUANWEN}It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.61,0:42:02.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,警察在来的路上了 我\N{\rYUANWEN}The police are on their way- - I'll
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.74,0:42:04.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会和你一起去苏格兰场录口供\N{\rYUANWEN}I'|| go to Scotland Yard with you to make a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.29,0:42:07.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不不不 我想现在就去\N{\rYUANWEN}No, no, no, no, I, I want to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.29,0:42:10.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你儿子在哪 特纳女士\N{\rYUANWEN}Where is your son, Miss Turner?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.38,0:42:14.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他离开伦敦了\N{\rYUANWEN}Um, he's left London.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.00,0:42:16.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我把一部分卖店的钱给了他\N{\rYUANWEN}I gave him the money from the sale of the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.50,0:42:18.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他 他往法国去了\N{\rYUANWEN}He's, um, he's heading to France.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.59,0:42:21.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,开始新的生活\N{\rYUANWEN}Start a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.97,0:42:26.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没必要等了 现在就走吧\N{\rYUANWEN}There's no sense in waiting- - let, let's go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.14,0:42:27.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\rYUANWEN}Just one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.22,0:42:28.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可是 拜托了\N{\rYUANWEN}But, pleasel
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.89,0:42:30.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我就是想赶紧了了这事儿\N{\rYUANWEN}I, I just want to get this over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.52,0:42:39.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,铃声是因为窗户开着有穿堂风\N{\rYUANWEN}The bells were caused by the draft from the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.49,0:42:41.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没什么好看的\N{\rYUANWEN}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.41,0:42:45.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,窗户都关着呢 特纳小小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}The window's not open, Miss Turner.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.07,0:42:47.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,麻烦你赶紧把我带去苏格兰场吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Will you please just take me to Scotland Yard
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.70,0:42:49.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这案子就能结了\N{\rYUANWEN}so this matter can be closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.30,0:43:03.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你儿子不在去法国的路上 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Your son isn't on his way to France, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.93,0:43:10.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他在哪里 特纳小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Where is he, Miss Turner?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.93,0:43:13.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不明白你在说什么\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.76,0:43:46.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,太荒唐了\N{\rYUANWEN}This is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.59,0:43:49.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他不在这里 也没做错任何事情\N{\rYUANWEN}He is not here, nor has he done anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.77,0:43:55.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\rYUANWEN}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.90,0:44:04.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哪也别想去 小子\N{\rYUANWEN}You're not going anywhere, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.57,0:44:05.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,阿尔伯特 不 求求你们\N{\rYUANWEN}Albert, no, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.99,0:44:07.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 求求了\N{\rYUANWEN}No, pleasel
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.07,0:44:08.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,带上马车\N{\rYUANWEN}Get him in the wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.41,0:44:10.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不要 求求你们了 放过我儿子吧\N{\rYUANWEN}No, please, please, let my boy go!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.08,0:44:12.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他不是故意做错事的\N{\rYUANWEN}He didn't mean to do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.08,0:44:13.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是个意外\N{\rYUANWEN}It was an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.58,0:44:14.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rYUANWEN}OFFICER: Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.58,0:44:16.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-不要  -妈\N{\rYUANWEN}Please! EDMUNDS: Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.71,0:44:18.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\rYUANWEN}: Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.08,0:44:20.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,帮帮我 妈\N{\rYUANWEN}EDMUNDS: Please help me, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.13,0:44:21.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\rYUANWEN}Please
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.30,0:44:26.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我刚满21岁\N{\rYUANWEN}EDMUNDS: I'd just turned 21
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.18,0:44:28.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,妈妈把真相告诉了我\N{\rYUANWEN}when my mother told me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.18,0:44:31.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,今年早些时候去世的那个男人\N{\rYUANWEN}That the man who died earlier this year
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.81,0:44:34.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不是我的亲生父亲\N{\rYUANWEN}wasn't my real father.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.35,0:44:36.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我其实很宽慰\N{\rYUANWEN}And I was relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.56,0:44:38.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是个可怕的酒鬼\N{\rYUANWEN}He was a horrible drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.52,0:44:40.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,让她的生活无比悲惨\N{\rYUANWEN}Led her a miserable life.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.98,0:44:42.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他接受了一个带着私生子的女人\N{\rYUANWEN}Taking on a woman with an illegitimate child
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.69,0:44:45.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就觉得自己可以为所欲为\N{\rYUANWEN}made him think he could do whatever he liked
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.90,0:44:48.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而她只能默默忍受\N{\rYUANWEN}and she would just have to put up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.78,0:44:50.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他死后 她改回了婚前姓氏\N{\rYUANWEN}When he died, she went back to her maiden name.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.53,0:44:52.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可想而知她有多恨他\N{\rYUANWEN}That's how much she hated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.58,0:44:55.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以你来伦敦是为了找亲生父亲\N{\rYUANWEN}So you came to London to find your real father?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.50,0:45:01.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,知道她骗了我后 我和她大吵一架 离开了家\N{\rYUANWEN}We'd rowed about the fact she'd lied to me, and I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.00,0:45:02.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我来到这里 在哈德卡斯尔的店里\N{\rYUANWEN}I traveled here and got a job
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.59,0:45:05.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,找了一份学徒的工作\N{\rYUANWEN}as an apprentice at Hardcastle's.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.13,0:45:07.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,几个月后 我鼓起勇气\N{\rYUANWEN}A few months later, I plucked up the courage
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.47,0:45:10.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,告诉了他我的真实身份\N{\rYUANWEN}and told him who I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.30,0:45:12.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我就是\N{\rYUANWEN}: I just
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.01,0:45:14.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想让他承认 他是我父亲\N{\rYUANWEN}wanted him to acknowledge he was my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.56,0:45:17.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我没想从他身上得到什么\N{\rYUANWEN}I didn't want anything from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.23,0:45:18.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但他没有认你\N{\rYUANWEN}But he rejected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.31,0:45:22.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我就去找了我舅 但他也把我拒之门外\N{\rYUANWEN}So, I went to see my uncle, and he turned me away, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.77,0:45:26.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我气得不得了\N{\rYUANWEN}and Igot so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.07,0:45:27.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这么多年来 他们是怎么对我妈的\N{\rYUANWEN}The way they'd treated my mother all these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.86,0:45:28.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在又是怎么对我的\N{\rYUANWEN}and now me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.16,0:45:32.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我怒火中烧 然后\N{\rYUANWEN}The fury just took me over, and,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.08,0:45:36.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就推了他\N{\rYUANWEN}and I, I pushed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.37,0:45:37.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他撞到了头\N{\rYUANWEN}And he hit his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.17,0:45:40.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那天你母亲也在城里\N{\rYUANWEN}Your mother was in town that day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.83,0:45:42.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不不不\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.13,0:45:44.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她和这件事情一点关系也没有 我发誓\N{\rYUANWEN}She had no part in this, I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.13,0:45:46.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她是来找我的\N{\rYUANWEN}She came looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.09,0:45:49.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她去了哈德卡斯尔的店里 发现他把我解雇了\N{\rYUANWEN}Went to Hardcastle's and found out he'd sacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.30,0:45:50.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她又花了好几天的时间\N{\rYUANWEN}She spent the next few days
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.68,0:45:51.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想找到我住的地方\N{\rYUANWEN}trying to find out where I was staying,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.68,0:45:56.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但伦敦太大了\N{\rYUANWEN}but London is a big place.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.02,0:45:57.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,马泽利找到我后\N{\rYUANWEN}When Mazelli got hold of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.68,0:45:59.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和我说他去过旅馆见过我妈\N{\rYUANWEN}he told me he'd been to visit my mother at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.69,0:46:01.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我这才知道她也在伦敦\N{\rYUANWEN}It was only then that I knew she was in town,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.52,0:46:02.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我就去找她了\N{\rYUANWEN}and I went to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.86,0:46:07.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我告诉了她我都去了哪里\N{\rYUANWEN}: I told her where I'd been.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.07,0:46:09.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,做了什么\N{\rYUANWEN}And what I'd done.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.32,0:46:10.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我需要我母亲\N{\rYUANWEN}I needed my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.99,0:46:14.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我需要她的帮助\N{\rYUANWEN}I needed her help.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.45,0:46:18.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是她这辈子唯一爱过她的男人\N{\rYUANWEN}I was the only man in her life who ever loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.91,0:46:21.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而现在我也让她伤心了\N{\rYUANWEN}And now I've broken her heart, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.39,0:46:41.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可怜的女人失去了她唯一的孩子\N{\rYUANWEN}That poor woman has lost the only child she had.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.69,0:46:43.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在无亲无故了\N{\rYUANWEN}She has no family now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.69,0:46:46.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道这种感觉\N{\rYUANWEN}I know what that's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.82,0:46:50.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我就是你的家人 威廉\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm your family, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.78,0:46:52.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不是像妹妹一样烦着你吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do I not annoy you like a younger sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.95,0:46:54.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,经常\N{\rYUANWEN}Frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.29,0:47:03.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不好意思打扰了头儿 但干草市场抢劫案\N{\rYUANWEN}Sorry to disturb, Skipper, but I've got news
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.58,0:47:05.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有新消息了 我的北方线人\N{\rYUANWEN}on the Haymarket robbery my snitch from up north
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.88,0:47:07.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,刚刚传来消息 提供了一个\N{\rYUANWEN}has just come through, he's given up
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.71,0:47:09.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,犯罪团伙可能的藏身之处\N{\rYUANWEN}a possible location where the gang are hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.42,0:47:11.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很好 查理\N{\rYUANWEN}Excellent, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.72,0:47:13.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,通知弟兄们马上来我办公室\N{\rYUANWEN}Alert the men to come to my office immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.68,0:47:14.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,同时告知上级\N{\rYUANWEN}and let the super know
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.93,0:47:16.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们将在第一时间进行突袭\N{\rYUANWEN}we'll carry out a raid first thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.18,0:47:17.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好的 头儿\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, Skip.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.43,0:47:19.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你忙吧\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll leave you to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.35,0:47:24.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伊莱沙 我在想\N{\rYUANWEN}Eliza, I was wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.98,0:47:27.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,明晚有时间一起吃晚饭吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Are you free to dine tomorrow evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.27,0:47:30.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我们刚吃过每月一次的晚餐呀\N{\rYUANWEN}But we've only just had our monthly dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.36,0:47:32.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你能忽略这一点 我也可以\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, I can overlook that if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.45,0:47:37.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那就明晚见吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Tomorrow evening it is, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.18,0:48:04.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和你做生意很愉快 波茨先生\N{\rYUANWEN}It was nice doing business with you, Mr. Potts.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.27,0:48:05.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, Miss Scarlet,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.69,0:48:07.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想说\N{\rYUANWEN}I, I'd like to say it was
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.48,0:48:09.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,真凶找到了 真让人松一口气\N{\rYUANWEN}It was a relief that the culprit was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.86,0:48:12.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哈德卡斯尔先生和他的放债人\N{\rYUANWEN}And that Mr. Hardcastle and his moneylender
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.32,0:48:14.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也都将受到相应处罚那么\N{\rYUANWEN}will also face some consequences, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.32,0:48:18.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那么是的 这是一个令人满意的结果\N{\rYUANWEN}So, yes, a satisfying conclusion all round.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.28,0:48:20.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如你所说 这是一个令人满意的结果\N{\rYUANWEN}It was, as you say, a, a satisfying conclusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.91,0:48:22.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我想知道 你对我处理案件的方式\N{\rYUANWEN}so I wonder if you have any comments
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.37,0:48:23.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有什么评价吗 波茨先生\N{\rYUANWEN}on my handling of the case, Mr. Potts.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.96,0:48:25.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.38,0:48:31.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你非常\N{\rYUANWEN}You did a very, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.63,0:48:34.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有能力 斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}capable job, Miss Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.01,0:48:36.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.22,0:48:38.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很开心我展现了专业能力\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm just happy to be able to demonstrate my professionalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.68,0:48:43.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要是以后 斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}So, if, in the future, Miss Scarlet
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.77,0:48:45.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,需要请你给予她\N{\rYUANWEN}did feel the need to call on you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.73,0:48:47.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,某些特别许可\N{\rYUANWEN}for some kind of dispensation,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.23,0:48:49.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比如\N{\rYUANWEN}for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.11,0:48:51.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,进入停尸房\N{\rYUANWEN}access to the mortuary,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.36,0:48:53.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,或许你会发现\N{\rYUANWEN}perhaps you will find that she's only
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.48,0:48:54.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她只有好意\N{\rYUANWEN}the very best of intentions
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.82,0:48:56.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对你的\N{\rYUANWEN}and poses no threat
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.95,0:48:58.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,规章制度毫无威胁 巴纳巴斯\N{\rYUANWEN}to your protocol, Barnabus.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.08,0:49:06.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那我们就说好了 从现在开始\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, perhaps we may agree that from...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.29,0:49:09.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你可以进入停尸房\N{\rYUANWEN}...now on you are able to enter the mortuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.25,0:49:16.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然得在警察的监督下\N{\rYUANWEN}Uh, under police supervision, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.05,0:49:22.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我得去工作了\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, I must be getting to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.60,0:49:24.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,晚餐不回来吃了 艾薇\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, and I won't be home for dinner, Ivy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.89,0:49:26.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,今晚约了威灵顿督察\N{\rYUANWEN}I will be dining with Inspector Wellington this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.06,0:49:29.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rYUANWEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.06,0:49:30.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没什么 就是想说\N{\rYUANWEN}Nothing, I just thought
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.65,0:49:32.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们不是刚吃过月度晚餐吗\N{\rYUANWEN}you had your monthly dinner quite recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.52,0:49:35.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,原来你还帮我记着呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Still keeping count, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.86,0:49:38.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,波茨先生回见\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Potts.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.45,0:49:39.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,斯嘉丽小姐回见\N{\rYUANWEN}Miss Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.57,0:49:44.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 亲爱的\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.72,0:50:01.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你去哪了\N{\rYUANWEN}Where've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.72,0:50:03.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,后援呢\N{\rYUANWEN}And where's the backup?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.05,0:50:04.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,坏消息 长官\N{\rYUANWEN}I've got bad news, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.64,0:50:06.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,上级把人手都调到哈顿花园了\N{\rYUANWEN}The super diverted the uniforms to Hatton Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.43,0:50:07.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,钻石抢劫案出了岔子\N{\rYUANWEN}Some diamond heist gone wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.81,0:50:09.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,据说死了三个人\N{\rYUANWEN}Three dead, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.10,0:50:11.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-如何  -我在后方转了一圈\N{\rYUANWEN}Well? PHELPS: I've been round the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.31,0:50:12.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看到他们正准备逃跑\N{\rYUANWEN}From what I can see, they're on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.69,0:50:14.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在收拾东西\N{\rYUANWEN}Gathering their things.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.32,0:50:15.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这可能是我们抓住这些渣滓的\N{\rYUANWEN}This might be the last chance we get
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.86,0:50:17.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,最后机会 头儿\N{\rYUANWEN}to nab these scum, Skipper.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.36,0:50:18.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但这里出口太多了 我们守不过来 长官\N{\rYUANWEN}But there's too many exits for us to cover, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.95,0:50:20.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,需要更多人手\N{\rYUANWEN}We need more men.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.20,0:50:28.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,准备袭击\N{\rYUANWEN}We're going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.66,0:50:30.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-查理你绕后 你和他一起  -是长官\N{\rYUANWEN}Charlie, you go around the back- - you, go with him. Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.79,0:50:33.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你从左边侧门进去\N{\rYUANWEN}You take the side entrance to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.17,0:50:34.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,菲茨罗伊 你跟着我  -从前门进\N{\rYUANWEN}Fitzroy, you're with me- - we'll go through the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.84,0:50:38.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,记住了 伙计们 我们的优势是出其不意\N{\rYUANWEN}Remember, lads, we have the advantage of surprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.01,0:50:39.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,让他们见识见识我们的本事\N{\rYUANWEN}so let's show them who they're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.47,0:50:41.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.05,0:50:42.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-好的长官  -是长官\N{\rYUANWEN}DETECTIVE: Yes, sir. DETECTIVE: Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.05,0:50:43.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,走\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.14,0:50:44.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,走吧 伙计\N{\rYUANWEN}PHELPS: Come on, lads.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.18,0:50:45.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好 上吧 兄弟\N{\rYUANWEN}DETECTIVE: Right, let's go, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.03,0:51:03.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,警察 放下武器\N{\rYUANWEN}WILLIAM: Police! Put down your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.87,0:51:05.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我说放下武器 马上\N{\rYUANWEN}I said put them down, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.02,0:51:38.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,菲茨罗伊警探\N{\rYUANWEN}Detective Fitzroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.27,0:51:40.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,斯嘉丽小姐\N{\rYUANWEN}: Miss Scarlet...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.19,0:51:42.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,伊莱沙\N{\rYUANWEN}Eliza.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.20,0:51:45.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,怎么了 出什么事了\N{\rYUANWEN}What is it? What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.32,0:51:48.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,威灵顿督察他\N{\rYUANWEN}It's Inspector Wellington.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.66,0:51:51.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他怎么了\N{\rYUANWEN}What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.54,0:51:54.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他中弹了\N{\rYUANWEN}: He's been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.25,0:51:58.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,正在做手术 但\N{\rYUANWEN}They're performing surgery, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.00,0:52:00.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,情况不乐观\N{\rYUANWEN}They're not optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.30,0:52:03.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,医生也不确定他能不能挺过来\N{\rYUANWEN}They cannot say for certain if he will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.65,0:52:17.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,丽兹\N{\rYUANWEN}Lizzie!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.77,0:52:18.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,下集预告\N你被赶出来了\N{\rYUANWEN}You've been expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.86,0:52:19.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你被赶出来了\N{\rYUANWEN}You've been expelled!
